item.description: Röyksopp - Sparks (Roni Size Remix) Pas sur Spotify / Dans mes fichiers

La chaine should be asleep dont je suis déjà tombé sur deux supers albums d’ambient japonaise. Brian Eno - Check out Ambient 1 - Music for airports & Apollo - Atmospheres & Soundtracks for a taste but he was pretty prolific as you can see on discogs.com Eno is perhaps the most important ambient artist ever, but imo, not the best. Check out Hakobune, Chihei Hatakeyama, and Endurance.
